Package Game

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Flying
    This interface represents those who are not affected by the power of gravity (e.i FALLING_SPEED
    Network
    This is an interface with basic methods to be used for players to send data to the server and receive data from it
    WorldConstants
    This interface contains a variety of constants used in the game
    WorldConstants.Frame
    This interface contains constants regarding the frame of the game
    WorldConstants.GROUND
    This interface contains constants regarding the ground
    WorldConstants.HEARTS
    This interface contains constants regarding the hearts of the players
    WorldConstants.PHYSICS
    This interface contains constants regarding the physics of the game
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FireAttack
    This class represents a fire attack which a Player can create.

    The FireAttack will move until it hits an opposing Player or reach the end of the screen.
    Heart
    This class represents a heart.
    Main
    This is the main class of the project.

    It handles the creation of the frame and the movement and actions of the characters
    MoveableCharacter
    This class represents a character in the game which has the ability to move.
    Player
    This class represents a player in the game.

    It handles its connection and communication to the server, its movement, its state (such as the amount of health left) and its actions (such as attacking the other characters)
    Sprite
    This class represents a sprite animation character.
    It handles the changing of the Sprite's costumes.
    Surface
    This class represents a surface which MoveableCharacter can stand on without falling
